    "Name": "Ojasan Assault Tank",
    "Details": "Developed during the Clan Invasion by Wakazashi Aerospace for the DCMS, the Ojasan is a slow and heavily armored tank designed to slug it out with Clan battlemechs and win. 14.5 tons of ferro-fibrous armor and a weapons loadout consiting of a Gauss Rifle and AC/20 combination; supported by a pair of Artemis IV enhanced LRM-15s enables it to crush anything in its way. A pair of ER Medium Lasers and a pair of Small Pulse Lasers round out the design.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Biome Restrictions: None.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 2/3 hexes / 60/90 meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Ferro-Fibrous\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       325     50\n<b>Left</b>         255     50\n<b>Right</b>       255     50\n<b>Rear</b>        205     50\n<b>Turret</b>      255     50\n\n<b>Total</b>      1295    250</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Main Battle Tank</color>",
    "Icon": "uixTxrIcon_ojasanassaulttank"
  },
